stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> open : new task created
    open --> in_progress : claim_next_dispatch_tasks
    open --> scheduled : due_at in future
    scheduled --> open : due_at reached
    in_progress --> delegated : Simone delegates to VP
    in_progress --> needs_review : ask human
    in_progress --> blocked : missing dependency
    delegated --> pending_review : VP finishes mission
    pending_review --> completed : Simone signs off
    pending_review --> in_progress : Simone rejects
    needs_review --> in_progress : human responds
    blocked --> in_progress : dependency cleared
    in_progress --> completed : direct finish (no delegation)
    in_progress --> parked : Simone shelves it
    completed --> [*] : completion_token written
    parked --> [*] : terminal (until manual revive)

    note right of completed
        completion_token prevents
        accidental re-entry to open
    end note

    note left of in_progress
        seizure_state column
        prevents double-dispatch
    end note
